cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >
  If you use or reference the Auracelle AI Governance Labs Simulation Suite,
  the Wargaming the Governance Asynchronously™ methodology, or any associated
  frameworks (E-AGPO-HT, E-AGSO-HT, E-IAIG-HT) in your research, publications,
  or policy work, please cite using the metadata below.

title: >
  Auracelle AI Governance Labs — Simulation Suite:
  Wargaming the Governance Asynchronously™

authors:
