abstract: >
  The Auracelle Simulation Suite is a proprietary asynchronous wargaming platform
  designed to stress-test AI governance policy, cyber resilience, standards
  verification, nuclear non-proliferation compliance, space governance, cognitive
  warfare readiness, and Arctic High North hybrid warfare diplomacy. The suite
  comprises seven simulation instruments — Stress Point (Charlie), Orion, Lyra,
  Delphi, Bach, Polaris, and WinterStorm2030 — underpinned by three proprietary
  frameworks: E-AGPO-HT (AI Governance Policy Optimization), E-AGSO-HT (AI
  Governance Standards Optimization), and E-IAIG-HT (Institutional AI Intelligence
  Governance). The platform operationalises the coined methodology of
  "stress-tested governance": revealing exactly where institutions fail before
  reality demands it.

keywords:
